<h1>Welcome</h1>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td colspan="3">
    <p>
    <strong>OpenGuides</strong> is a network of free, community-maintained "wiki" city guides
    to which anyone can contribute.<br>&nbsp;
    </p></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="33%"><p>
    <span class="red"><strong>News:</strong></span><br>
